---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About — AI Dictionary" description="Learn about AI Dictionary, The ABCs of Everything — a comprehensive, LLM-friendly dictionary of technology terms.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pt-12 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-black mb-8">
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-brand via-red-brand to-orange-brand bg-clip-text text-transparent">About</span>
    </h1>

    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        <strong class="text-body">AI Dictionary</strong> is <em>The ABCs of Everything</em> — a comprehensive, beautifully designed dictionary covering technology, artificial intelligence, machine learning, design, business, programming, web development, data science, cybersecurity, cloud computing, DevOps, and UX/UI.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-body mt-10 mb-4">🤖 Built for Humans & Machines</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Every definition is written to be clear and concise — 1-3 sentences that give you the essential understanding. Terms include category tags and cross-references to related concepts.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        This site is also designed to be <strong>LLM-friendly</strong>. Following the <code>llms.txt</code> convention, we provide structured, machine-readable content that AI systems can easily parse:
      </p>
      <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li><a href="/llms.txt" class="text-pink-brand font-medium hover:underline">/llms.txt</a> — Structured index of all content pages</li>
        <li><a href="/llms-full.txt" class="text-pink-brand font-medium hover:underline">/llms-full.txt</a> — Complete dictionary in plain text</li>
        <li><a href="/api/terms.json" class="text-pink-brand font-medium hover:underline">/api/terms.json</a> — Full dictionary as JSON API</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-body mt-10 mb-4">🎨 Design</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Inspired by bold typographic poster design, AI Dictionary uses gradient colors from hot pink through red and orange to yellow, with highlighted term names and clean multi-column layouts reminiscent of traditional print dictionaries.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-body mt-10 mb-4">🛠 Technical</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Built with Astro and Tailwind CSS for maximum performance — every page is static HTML with zero JavaScript required for core content. Semantic HTML, JSON-LD structured data, and clean URLs make the content accessible to search engines and AI systems alike.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-body mt-10 mb-4">🌍 Open & Extensible</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Content is stored in structured JSON files, designed for easy internationalization. The architecture supports multiple languages — contributions welcome.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Base>
